Justin Shenkarow https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Justin_Shenkarow 0 Justin Moran Shenkarow (born October 17, 1980) is an American actor, voice actor, producer, writer and director best known for his roles of Matthew Brock in Picket Fences, Simon Holmes in Eerie, Indiana, and the voice of Harold Berman on Hey Arnold!.
